<P>
	In a Nielsen Media Research ranking of the top programs on basic  
cable networks that ran Thursday, The Associated Press reported the 
wrong dates for the period covered. 
</P>
<P>
	The list encompassed programs during the week of May 3-9, not  
April 19-25. 



